column2: Tenioha! 2: Limit Over - Mada Mada Ippai, Ecchi Shiyo? The Animation

What started as a normal student life turns into a crazy sex fueled dreamland with every female he knows wanting a piece of him! In the end he lands himself in a foursome with all of the girls in question and doesn't even know where to begin!
